In [[Lightsaber combat/Legends|lightsaber combat]], '''''shun''''' was a 360-degree turn performed with just a one-handed grip, thus gaining speed for an attack.

[[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] used this move on the [[Bellassan]] insurgent [[Roan Lands]], fatally wounding him in the process.

